      "content": "i was looking at some old photos today. it's weird. i don't even recognize that person. it feels like the version of me that actually mattered, the one with all the potential and the spark... that person died a long time ago. now i'm just kind of a ghost inhabiting a body that keeps moving through the motions. just a walking corpse.",
